{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/media-S3/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"hongo"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"445991a3-c7e5-5f30-aa17-c911ead116fd","excerpt":"S3 버킷 생성 Django setting 설정 패키지 & 라이브러리 설치 settings.py - INSTALLED_APP","html":"<h2>S3 버킷 생성</h2>\n<h2>Django setting 설정</h2>\n<h4>패키지 &#x26; 라이브러리 설치</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">pip install boto3 <span class=\"token comment\"># python에서 AWS에 접근가능한 패키지</span>\npip install django<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>storages <span class=\"token comment\"># 커스텀 스토리지 </span></code></pre></div>\n<h4>settings.py - INSTALLED_APP</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># media url 설정</span>\nMEDIA_URL <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/media/\"</span>\nMEDIA_ROOT <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>join<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>BASE_DIR<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'media'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># for AWS S3</span>\nDEFAULT_FILE_STORAGE <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'storages.backends.s3boto3.S3Boto3Storage'</span>\nAWS_S3_SECURE_URLS <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">False</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># use http instead of https</span>\nAWS_QUERYSTRING_AUTH <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">False</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># don't add complex authentication-related query parameters for requests</span>\n\nload_dotenv<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># AWS IAM 유저 key설정</span>\nAWS_S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>getenv<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ACCESS_KEY'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nAWS_S3_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY <span class=\"token operator\">=</span>os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>getenv<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'SECRET_ACCESS_KEY'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># S3 버킷 이름</span>\nAWS_STORAGE_BUCKET_NAME <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'danmer-videos'</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"django media파일 S3서버랑 연동하기","date":"May 08, 2022","update":null,"tags":["DRF","AWS","S3"],"series":"종설"},"fields":{"slug":"/media-S3/","readingTime":{"minutes":0.585}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"445991a3-c7e5-5f30-aa17-c911ead116fd","fields":{"slug":"/media-S3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"django media파일 S3서버랑 연동하기"}}},{"node":{"id":"100231f0-4961-5059-8668-1f8f59ef0da1","fields":{"slug":"/deploy-ec2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"django 프로젝트 ec2로 배포하기"}}},{"node":{"id":"f58bb59a-6a17-5889-a8ef-51796e6883ec","fields":{"slug":"/pm2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"django에서 pm2 사용하기"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/sync-tools/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"os 10-1 Synchronization Tools"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/deploy-ec2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"django 프로젝트 ec2로 배포하기"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"445991a3-c7e5-5f30-aa17-c911ead116fd","series":"종설","previousPostId":"a1a1c386-4e12-55c0-b88e-b1ab29cfc979","nextPostId":"100231f0-4961-5059-8668-1f8f59ef0da1"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}